text: Erest up on see on hamberghes þanne on smaledich on merkemere.
Þannen south endelang dich on bremelwil.
Þanen of bremelwille on aishwel on þe hamheved.
Þanen up endelang rewe on þe ellene stubbis.
Þanen so bi heved on smalelinchewey of þan weye on bradenwel on merepul of merepulle on bisschopiswerthe.
And so endlang pillis on axen.
